name: Jigsaw Manor.
description: Jigsaw Manor is my 4th jigsaw puzzle. In this return to this series I decided to explore and forshadow my next NFT, which will be the last chapter of a 3 part point and click game called "Chapter 3: The Manor". By solving this puzzle, you'll unlock a small video, whose graphic look was inspired by the old 1st person games from the 90s. I hope you like it!
